<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<title>multicol | the number and width of columns</title>
<link rel="author" title="Hakon Wium Lie" href="mailto:howcome@opera.com"/>
<style type="text/css">
div { 
  font: 10px/10px Ahem;
  margin: 1em;
  color: red;
  background: yellow;
  border: thin solid black;
  width: 300px;
}

div.multicol {
  column-width: 101px;
  column-gap: 0;
  column-rule: none;
  orphans: 0;
  widows: 0;
}
span { color: green }
</style>
</head>
<body>
The two boxes below should be identical.

<div>
x x x x x x x x<span>x x x x x x x x </span><br/>
x x x x x x x x<span>x x x x x x x x </span>
</div>

<div>
x x x x x x x x<span>x x x x x x x x </span><br/>
x x x x x x x x<span>x x x x x x x x </span>
</div>
</body>
</html>
